* sandwich NEWS
** 0.3.0 (2011-10-17)

 - Add -e option
 - Add support for cookbooks: sandwich can now load other cookbooks
 - Show chef version in --version output
 - Change default log level from "warn" to "error"
 - Change cookbook file lookup to work relative to sandwich scripts,
   fixes #6

** 0.2.0 (2011-09-07)

 - Add support for cookbook_file and template resources
 - Add support for standalone sandwich scripts: sandwich can now be
   used in shebang lines
 - Save file caches and file backups to ~/.cache/sandwich instead of
   /var/cache/chef for non-root users, fixes #3
 - Report correct recipe filename in error messages, fixes #2

** 0.1.0 (2011-08-09)

 - First release

